Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來的除了我…還有兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向我靠近  這個速度是昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.42,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(953,505)\bord0.5}薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答錯了  是我薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？為什麼幾乎毫髮無損？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.81,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(227,92)\fad(0,80)\bord0.5\fs34}昴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.81,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(339,294)\fad(0,80)\fs30}從SLB-PS下保護薇薇歐  無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧  這就是特救魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.73,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(834,479)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs34}諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.73,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(942,680)\fad(80,0)\fs30}SLB命中後被薇薇歐攻擊擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞娜小姐  我要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是別過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斷（暫定）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:47.88,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,80)\pos(241,517)\bord0.5}愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐同學  我不會讓你靠近迪亞娜小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那下就已經被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐向迪亞娜發射了什麼對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(755,646)\fs36}Sonic Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  單發的音速射手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐同學  好像就剩我們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我要上了  愛因哈特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶對手的攻擊並做出對策的學習能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而精密的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懼怕對手攻擊  反而挺身出拳的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是防守反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這  一閃必中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Accel Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅疾破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.07,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(241,89)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs30}薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.07,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(241,250)\fad(80,0)\fs30}擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.07,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1043,522)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs30}愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.07,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1043,683)\fad(80,0)\fs30}擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  比賽結束
